These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: indonesian, japanese, turkish, colombian
Food: grapefruit, kiwi, cherry, peach
1. Food:peach is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
2. Nationality:indonesian is on the left of Food:kiwi##1
3. Nationality:colombian is in an odd position##4
4. Food:cherry is on the left or right of Food:peach##3
5. Nationality:indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | colombian | turkish |
| Food        | grapefruit | kiwi   | peach | cherry    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: soy-milk, 7up, fanta, coffee
Job: musician, social-worker, fisherman, software-developer
1. Beverage:7up is on the left of Beverage:coffee##1
2. Job:musician is on the left of Job:fisherman##1
3. Job:fisherman is in an odd position##4
4. Job:musician == Beverage:soy-milk##1
5. Job:social-worker is on the right of Job:fisherman##1
6. Job:musician == Beverage:soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk  | 7up  | coffee |
| Job   | software-developer    | musician | fisherman | social-worker    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: soccer, weightlifting, climbing, volleyball
Game: chess, whist, snooker, domino
1. Sport:volleyball is on the left or right of Game:domino##3
2. Sport:climbing is in an even position##4
3. Game:domino is on the left or right of Sport:weightlifting##3
4. Game:domino is on the right of Game:snooker##1
5. Game:chess is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:weightlifting is on the right of Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | volleyball | climbing | weightlifting    | soccer      |
| Game   | snooker        | domino     | chess | whist |

