.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
House: wooden, cottage, victorian, futuristic
Nationality: russian, american, nigerian, japanese
1. House:cottage is between Nationality:russian and Nationality:japanese##2
2. House:futuristic is on the left of House:wooden##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:japanese##1
5. Nationality:american is on the right of House:wooden##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House         | futuristic | wooden | cottage | victorian |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | russian   | american    | japanese  |

