.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Pet: lizard, snake, hedgehog, frog
Food: papaya, artichoke, kale, lemon
1. Pet:hedgehog is on the right of Food:lemon##1
2. Food:artichoke == Pet:frog##1
3. Food:kale is on the right of Pet:lizard##1
4. Pet:snake is on the far left##1
5. Pet:hedgehog is in an odd position##4
6. Food:papaya is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | snake  | lizard    | hedgehog   | frog       |
| Food   | papaya | lemon | kale | artichoke |

