.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
Flower: poppy, rose, aconite, begonia
Music-Genre: folk, metal, ambient, dubstep
1. Music-Genre:dubstep is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:ambient is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1
3. Flower:begonia is on the left of Flower:aconite##1
4. Music-Genre:dubstep == Flower:poppy##1
5. Flower:begonia is on the left or right of Music-Genre:folk##3
6. Music-Genre:metal is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower   | poppy | begonia | aconite | rose    |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep | ambient  | folk     | metal |

