2. City:nizza is in an odd position##4
3. Food:potato is on the left or right of City:nizza##3
4. City:nizza is on the right of Food:potato##1
5. City:edinburgh is between City:nizza and City:miami##2
6. Food:tomato is in an odd position##4
7. Food:tomato is between City:edinburgh and Food:apricot##2
8. City:edinburgh is on the left or right of City:miami##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| City   | miami | edinburgh      | nizza | hannover |
| Food   | onion  | potato | tomato    | apricot            |

