.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Food: cranberry, cabbage, spinach, zucchini
Movie-Genre: comedy, drama, mystery, sports
1. Food:cranberry == Movie-Genre:sports##1
2. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the right of Food:cranberry##1
3. Movie-Genre:sports is between Movie-Genre:comedy and Food:spinach##2
4. Food:cranberry is in an odd position##4
5. Movie-Genre:sports is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:comedy##3
6. Food:cabbage is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:drama##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Food      | cabbage       | spinach   | cranberry | zucchini |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | drama | sports        | comedy    |

