.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
Transport: quad-bike, bus, snowmobile, train
City: venice, colone, london, miami
1. Transport:quad-bike is between City:venice and Transport:bus##2
2. Transport:snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
3. Transport:bus is on the left of City:miami##1
4. Transport:train is on the left of Transport:bus##1
5. City:miami is in an odd position##4
6. City:london is on the left of City:colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Transport   | train | bus         | quad-bike   | snowmobile |
| City   | london    | colone | miami | venice   |

