.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
Transport: car, roller, quad-bike, bike
Job: electrician, social-worker, mechanic, police-officer
1. Job:police-officer == Transport:quad-bike##1
2. Job:mechanic == Transport:car##1
3. Job:social-worker == Transport:bike##1
4. Transport:quad-bike is on the left or right of Transport:bike##3
5. Transport:car is in an even position##4
6. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Job:mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Transport   | roller | car | quad-bike    | bike |
| Job   | electrician   | mechanic  | police-officer | social-worker     |

