.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
Movie-Genre: horror, fantasy, musical, drama
Birthday: april, february, march, august
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:horror##1
2. Movie-Genre:musical is in an even position##4
3. Birthday:february == Movie-Genre:musical##1
4. Birthday:march is on the left or right of Birthday:february##3
5. Birthday:february is between Birthday:august and Birthday:march##2
6. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the right of Birthday:august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | drama   | musical | horror | fantasy    |
| Birthday   | march | february  | august     | april |

