.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, wooden, farmhouse
Movie-Genre: animation, disaster, musical, satire
1. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the far left##1
2. House:wooden is on the left or right of House:craftsman##3
3. House:farmhouse is on the far left or far right##3
4. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1
5. Movie-Genre:satire is on the right of House:craftsman##1
6. Movie-Genre:musical is in an even position##4
7. Movie-Genre:animation == House:gothic-revival##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| House   | farmhouse | craftsman    | wooden       | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre       | disaster  | musical | satire | animation  |

