.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, comedy, time-travel, romance
Color: green, ebony, mauve, blood-red
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left or right of Color:green##3
3. Color:ebony is between Movie-Genre:adventure and Color:green##2
4. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the far left or far right##3
5. Color:mauve is on the right of Movie-Genre:romance##1
6. Color:mauve is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | time-travel   | romance | comedy |
| Color   | blood-red          | ebony | green         | mauve  |

 